author: Joshua Fluke
description:
Check out Filmora here! - https://bit.ly/4k60z8H

From porta-potty entrepreneurs to Kitchen Nightmares for dentists, the world of corporate podcasts is absolutely insane. Welcome to LinkedIn’s version of Interdimensional Cable, where buzzwords fly and nobody really knows what they’re talking about. In this video, we explore the wildest and most cringe-worthy corporate podcasts out there.

Featuring:
Car wash CEO updates
The portable restroom podcast
Dental acquisitions gone wrong
Corporate jargon that means nothing
